[src:1152/1070] Year **1070** (**MLXX**) was a common year starting on Friday of the Julian calendar, the 1070th year of the Common Era (CE) and *Anno Domini* (AD) designations, the 70th year of the 2nd millennium, the 70th year of the 11th century, and the 1st year of the 1070s decade.
[src:1152/1080] Year **1080** (**MLXXX**) was a leap year starting on Wednesday of the Julian calendar.
[src:1152/1090] Year **1090** (**MXC**) was a common year starting on Tuesday of the Julian calendar.
[src:1152/1104] Year **1104** (**MCIV**) was a leap year starting on Friday of the Julian calendar.
[src:1152/1129] Year **1129** (**MCXXIX**) was a common year starting on Tuesday of the Julian calendar.
[src:1152/1130s] The **1130s** was a decade of the Julian Calendar which began on January 1, 1130, and ended on December 31, 1139.
[src:1152/1140s-p01] The **1140s** was a decade of the Julian Calendar which began on January 1, 1140, and ended on December 31, 1149.
[src:1152/1152] Year **1152** (**MCLII**) was a leap year starting on Tuesday of the Julian calendar.
